## Development Acknowledgment

This project was developed with assistance from Anthropic's Claude Code, which provided
architectural guidance, code review, debugging support, and documentation assistance.

## Third-Party Libraries

This project uses the following third-party libraries:
- AccelStepper Library (Mike McCauley) - Stepper motor control
- FastLED Library - WS2812B LED strip control
- Arduino ESP32 Core - ESP32 microcontroller support

These libraries are subject to their respective licenses.